Package controller

Provides classes for the controllers connecting the front- and back-ends of the game
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIBehaviorController
    Class providing the controller for the processes related to the selection of the intelligence level of the agent
    InitScreenController
    Class providing the controller for the processes related to setting up the board: specifying the dimensions and the locations of the beacon tiles, pit tiles, and the gold tile
    MainScreenController
    Class providing the controller for the processes related to the main screen of the system (that is, the board together with the pertinent statistics)
    SystemBehaviorController
    Class providing the controller for the processes related to the selection of the speed at which the actions of the agent are displayed
